      "file_path": "main/src/test/java/org/onap/policy/api/main/rest/provider/TestPolicyProvider.java",
      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 68,
      "message": "Or a random ordering problem - if I recall policy/engine had these issues because they were built on a developers machine that ran them in a specific order. Running on someone else's machine (usually my MAC!) would show random failures. Some best practice is to either require ordering, or have shutdown/start methods to assure a clean environment is there for each test.",
